@startuml
title CSV chunk ordering and final merge

participant "ExportNewsMessageHandler" as Handler
participant "NewsExportCsvStorage" as Storage
participant "MinIO / S3" as S3

Handler -> Storage: writeChunk(exportId, sortedNews)
Storage -> Storage: startNewsId = first news id
Storage -> S3: write news-exports/{id}/chunks/{startNewsId padded}.csv

...

Storage -> S3: list news-exports/{id}/chunks
S3 --> Storage: chunk paths
Storage -> Storage: sort chunk paths by filename
Storage -> Storage: write CSV header
loop each chunk in order
    Storage -> S3: read chunk
    Storage -> Storage: append chunk body
end
Storage -> S3: write news-exports/{id}/news-export-{id}.csv
Storage -> S3: delete temporary chunks

@enduml
